Title: An Act Changing the Name of San Pablo Elementary School in the Municipality of Manapla, Province of Negros Occidental, to Don Emilio Miraflores, Sr. Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 817
An Act Changing the Name of San Pablo Elementary School in the Municipality of Manapla, Province of Negros Occidental, to Don Emilio Miraflores, Sr. Memorial School
Section 1. The name of San Pablo Elementary School in the Municipality of Manapla, Province of Negros Occidental, is changed to Don Emilio Miraflores, Sr. Memorial School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: April 27, 1984
